description.displayText: I used to work with her as a fellow counselor in an after school program. She's a good listener and knows how to multitask very well. She took care of my two Dachshund dogs for me when I was away when needed. She also kept my house in good shape which included general overall cleaning in all rooms in the house as well as laundry. I was satisfied with her work ethic.

description.displayText: She has cared for both my daughters and our cat. She was very efficient at making sure my girls were fed, bathed and had homework done. She was also very attentive to my cat and he seems very fond of her. It was an overall excellent experience. I definitely recommend her.
